{"tid":2233102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國加州中學管弦樂團網上合奏榮光","createTime":"2020-10-07T01:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T12:58:48.000Z","uid":123774,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb86c5ac9c975de0f89ad646b47d0e96f31ab035","tid":2233102,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"From Studio Incento:<br />\n<br />\n美國加州一所公立高中 Amador Valley High School 管弦樂團超過50位同學，在疫情隔離期間，網上合奏了「願榮光歸香港」。該所高中的音樂總監的妻子是香港人，音樂總監叫同學仔演奏此曲作為他們「Songs of Protest」program 的其中一曲。喺自由的國度讀書真好，小編聽到毛管棟🥺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好聽到起雞皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JDGkKS67VS8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJDGkKS67VS8&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=02e8d1f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JDGkKS67VS8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1474101479504603/posts/2725035414411197/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1474101479504603%2Fposts%2F2725035414411197%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=2dea4ea7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1474101479504603/posts/2725035414411197/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"882292fdae37c22dbad3414b14b30dd783286d6d","tid":2233102,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等你班友仲敢唔敢鬧人左膠"},{"pid":"76a2a74640767646707c745fdb82cf92726f470c","tid":2233102,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"👍🏾"},{"pid":"aac79988b4d6bc4effd28343bfc203da37493145","tid":2233102,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}